1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 27]

2
00:00:25,975 --> 00:00:26,694
Don't be nervous.

3
00:00:27,855 --> 00:00:29,214
I'm just testing this gun.

4
00:00:41,695 --> 00:00:42,694
Is there evidence to take down

5
00:00:43,455 --> 00:00:44,654
Zhou Quan with Zhang Jinbao?

6
00:00:45,295 --> 00:00:45,694
Right.

7
00:00:47,975 --> 00:00:49,654
I've actually always been curious.

8
00:00:50,815 --> 00:00:51,894
When did you become

9
00:00:51,895 --> 00:00:53,894
a cold-blooded killer?

10
00:00:54,695 --> 00:00:55,694
Why exactly

11
00:00:56,615 --> 00:00:58,334
did you go down this path of no return?

12
00:01:10,175 --> 00:01:10,974
This is

13
00:01:11,175 --> 00:01:11,814
the maid

14
00:01:11,815 --> 00:01:13,454
Mother just brought back.

15
00:01:13,615 --> 00:01:14,814
Isn't this just a kid?

16
00:01:15,175 --> 00:01:16,454
What work can she do at this age?

17
00:01:17,095 --> 00:01:18,254
I can work!

18
00:01:18,455 --> 00:01:19,254
I can cook,

19
00:01:19,735 --> 00:01:20,454
mop floors,

20
00:01:20,455 --> 00:01:21,374
and sew clothes!

21
00:01:21,895 --> 00:01:22,814
Please,

22
00:01:22,975 --> 00:01:24,054
Don't sell me.

23
00:01:24,335 --> 00:01:25,334
You can cook?

24
00:01:25,535 --> 00:01:26,814
You can cook at this age?

25
00:01:26,975 --> 00:01:28,614
I can stand on a stool to cook.

26
00:01:29,095 --> 00:01:30,974
I wash vegetables really clean!

27
00:01:31,335 --> 00:01:32,974
I can also clean rooms,

28
00:01:33,455 --> 00:01:34,094
and also...

29
00:01:34,695 --> 00:01:35,334
and also...

30
00:01:36,095 --> 00:01:36,894
Don't worry,

31
00:01:36,895 --> 00:01:38,174
we won't sell you.

32
00:01:38,695 --> 00:01:39,734
Come on, let's go play.

33
00:01:40,735 --> 00:01:42,454
But I still have work to do.

34
00:01:42,815 --> 00:01:43,734
What are you worried about?

35
00:01:43,735 --> 00:01:45,054
Later we'll just say

36
00:01:45,055 --> 00:01:46,334
you've already cleaned here.

37
00:01:46,535 --> 00:01:46,974
Come on.

38
00:01:47,095 --> 00:01:47,894
Let's go check it out.

39
00:01:48,055 --> 00:01:49,094
When I just arrived at the Zhou residence,

40
00:01:49,095 --> 00:01:50,254
I met you both.

41
00:01:50,255 --> 00:01:51,334
I thought I had found

42
00:01:51,335 --> 00:01:53,334
the two best older brothers in the world.

43
00:01:53,375 --> 00:01:54,894
Until she appeared.

44
00:01:55,535 --> 00:01:56,534
Hello, Young Master.

45
00:01:58,095 --> 00:01:58,974
Nanxi, here.

46
00:02:00,535 --> 00:02:01,454
So much?

47
00:02:01,535 --> 00:02:02,534
Thank you, Young Master.

48
00:02:02,695 --> 00:02:04,614
Share these with the girls in the courtyard.

49
00:02:04,975 --> 00:02:05,694
From now on,

50
00:02:05,735 --> 00:02:06,974
put in a good word for me more often.

51
00:02:07,695 --> 00:02:09,054
Pick a nice one for Chuxue.

52
00:02:09,335 --> 00:02:09,934
Okay.

53
00:02:14,135 --> 00:02:14,734
Take it.

54
00:02:18,855 --> 00:02:20,054
Tonight, An He

55
00:02:20,055 --> 00:02:21,774
is performing at Qingfeng theater.

56
00:02:22,055 --> 00:02:22,934
I paid extra

57
00:02:22,935 --> 00:02:24,134
to get these tickets.

58
00:02:24,455 --> 00:02:25,334
Come with me.

59
00:02:25,575 --> 00:02:26,214
Young Master,

60
00:02:26,495 --> 00:02:28,214
I love listening to An He's performances.

61
00:02:28,455 --> 00:02:29,894
Can you take me too?

62
00:02:30,055 --> 00:02:31,294
You always take her.

63
00:02:39,655 --> 00:02:40,614
I only have two tickets.

64
00:02:46,935 --> 00:02:47,574
Let's go.

65
00:02:48,575 --> 00:02:49,294
Young Master,

66
00:02:49,855 --> 00:02:52,014
I still have lots of chores to finish.

67
00:02:52,215 --> 00:02:53,054
I still need to

68
00:02:53,055 --> 00:02:54,494
deliver ointment to Second Concubine.

69
00:02:54,735 --> 00:02:55,854
Isn't Nanxi here?

70
00:02:57,735 --> 00:02:58,414
Nanxi,

71
00:02:58,855 --> 00:02:59,654
deliver the ointment

72
00:02:59,655 --> 00:03:00,734
to Second Concubine later.

73
00:03:00,855 --> 00:03:01,454
Okay.

74
00:03:02,175 --> 00:03:02,734
Let's go.

75
00:03:04,575 --> 00:03:05,894
An He specifically instructed

76
00:03:05,895 --> 00:03:07,334
to save the best seat for you.

77
00:03:07,575 --> 00:03:09,574
I'm just tagging along.

78
00:03:17,575 --> 00:03:18,294
Nanxi?

79
00:03:19,215 --> 00:03:20,014
Second Young Master.

80
00:03:20,455 --> 00:03:21,494
Why are you alone here?

81
00:03:21,895 --> 00:03:22,854
Where's Chuxue?

82
00:03:24,415 --> 00:03:26,054
She went to see the opera with the Eldest Young Master.

83
00:03:30,455 --> 00:03:31,934
Gone to see that actor again.

84
00:03:34,735 --> 00:03:35,174
By the way,

85
00:03:35,855 --> 00:03:37,334
didn't you also enjoy watching opera?

86
00:03:37,735 --> 00:03:38,934
Why didn't you go along?

87
00:03:40,935 --> 00:03:42,054
I'm very busy.

88
00:03:42,335 --> 00:03:43,014
Later, I need to

89
00:03:43,015 --> 00:03:44,894
deliver ointment to Second Concubine.

90
00:03:45,335 --> 00:03:47,054
So I let the Eldest Young Master take her.

91
00:03:50,775 --> 00:03:51,574
Second Young Master,

92
00:03:52,055 --> 00:03:53,574
why did you change your scent pouch?

93
00:03:54,015 --> 00:03:55,454
What about the one I embroidered for you earlier?

94
00:03:56,735 --> 00:03:58,014
Chuxue said the scent pouch

95
00:03:58,215 --> 00:03:59,574
you embroidered for me was old,

96
00:03:59,775 --> 00:04:01,174
so she made me a new one.

97
00:04:03,895 --> 00:04:04,774
She replaced it.

98
00:04:06,655 --> 00:04:07,414
Looks good, right?

99
00:04:08,575 --> 00:04:09,174
Good.

100
00:04:09,655 --> 00:04:10,494
You're busy.

101
00:04:10,615 --> 00:04:11,174
I'll leave.

102
00:04:28,295 --> 00:04:29,734
Actually, all along,

103
00:04:31,095 --> 00:04:33,414
I've really wanted a brother like you.

104
00:04:34,295 --> 00:04:35,454
But what I didn't expect was that

105
00:04:36,615 --> 00:04:37,854
Ye Chuxue died,

106
00:04:38,295 --> 00:04:39,534
and the entire Zhou household acted

107
00:04:39,535 --> 00:04:41,054
as if nothing had happened.

108
00:04:43,855 --> 00:04:44,974
Only you went to

109
00:04:44,975 --> 00:04:46,294
the police station

110
00:04:47,335 --> 00:04:47,894
to ask about the case's progress

111
00:04:47,895 --> 00:04:49,894
in the beginning.

112
00:04:53,215 --> 00:04:55,054
No one else ever mentioned her again.

113
00:04:56,295 --> 00:04:57,614
Isn't that just what you wanted?

114
00:04:58,615 --> 00:04:59,454
Or did you hope

115
00:04:59,455 --> 00:05:01,334
everyone would dig to the bottom of this?

116
00:05:01,855 --> 00:05:03,174
I had a complete plan

117
00:05:03,295 --> 00:05:04,854
for this matter.

118
00:05:05,335 --> 00:05:06,094
Including the steward,

119
00:05:06,095 --> 00:05:07,094
including the handwriting,

120
00:05:07,655 --> 00:05:09,054
but what I didn't expect was,

121
00:05:10,975 --> 00:05:12,894
that no one would actually investigate.

122
00:05:16,415 --> 00:05:17,614
It was at that moment

123
00:05:17,775 --> 00:05:18,854
that I realized,

124
00:05:20,455 --> 00:05:21,294
a maid

125
00:05:22,335 --> 00:05:24,054
in the end, she's just a maid.

126
00:05:26,055 --> 00:05:27,894
Even if favored by her master,

127
00:05:29,175 --> 00:05:31,734
she's no different from a favorite dog.

128
00:05:32,615 --> 00:05:34,094
I must climb higher.

129
00:05:34,775 --> 00:05:36,294
I don't want to be a maid anymore.

130
00:05:37,055 --> 00:05:38,454
I want to be a noble.

131
00:05:39,455 --> 00:05:40,534
You set me up just to

132
00:05:41,175 --> 00:05:42,974
become a concubine of the Zhou family?

133
00:05:49,615 --> 00:05:50,454
Actually,

134
00:05:52,055 --> 00:05:53,054
when Jinbao told me

135
00:05:53,055 --> 00:05:54,614
you were Master He,

136
00:05:55,855 --> 00:05:56,734
I didn't intend to use

137
00:05:56,735 --> 00:05:58,094
this method to trap you.

138
00:05:58,855 --> 00:05:59,894
Because in you,

139
00:06:00,975 --> 00:06:02,054
I truly saw

140
00:06:02,055 --> 00:06:03,774
hope of controlling my own destiny.

141
00:06:06,295 --> 00:06:08,894
But the blame lies with Ye Zhiqiu.

142
00:06:09,775 --> 00:06:11,614
She insisted on investigating the handwriting with you,

143
00:06:11,615 --> 00:06:12,614
and wanted to find Third Concubine,

144
00:06:12,615 --> 00:06:13,974
to ask about my whereabouts three years ago.

145
00:06:15,175 --> 00:06:16,774
She is too clever.

146
00:06:17,095 --> 00:06:18,774
She would definitely discover my crime.

147
00:06:19,615 --> 00:06:20,854
Third Concubine's death

148
00:06:21,055 --> 00:06:22,414
is all Ye Zhiqiu's fault.

149
00:06:22,535 --> 00:06:23,334
Everything is because of her.

150
00:06:23,335 --> 00:06:24,654
She forced me.

151
00:06:24,655 --> 00:06:25,734
Why are you here?

152
00:06:27,895 --> 00:06:28,734
Actually,

153
00:06:28,975 --> 00:06:30,294
I could have dealt with her.

154
00:06:32,615 --> 00:06:34,094
But just at this moment,

155
00:06:36,335 --> 00:06:38,174
I became pregnant with Zhang Jinbao's child.

156
00:06:39,215 --> 00:06:41,454
I had no choice but to drive a wedge between you.

157
00:06:42,215 --> 00:06:43,614
Only I, Nanxi,

158
00:06:44,615 --> 00:06:46,414
carrying your child, Zhou Yimo,

159
00:06:47,175 --> 00:06:49,174
could have complete security.

160
00:06:49,735 --> 00:06:51,654
Ye Zhiqiu forced me.

161
00:06:52,175 --> 00:06:53,414
I had no choice.

162
00:07:02,615 --> 00:07:03,454
But

163
00:07:04,455 --> 00:07:06,214
now nothing matters anymore.

164
00:07:06,975 --> 00:07:07,534
Money,

165
00:07:08,975 --> 00:07:09,534
freedom,

166
00:07:10,295 --> 00:07:11,094
and my child.

167
00:07:15,055 --> 00:07:17,854
And safety in this chaotic world.

168
00:07:19,415 --> 00:07:20,454
I, Nanxi,

169
00:07:21,295 --> 00:07:23,534
can finally start a new life.

170
00:07:29,175 --> 00:07:30,734
Then I must congratulate you.

171
00:07:32,975 --> 00:07:34,094
The evidence is inside.

172
00:07:34,975 --> 00:07:36,214
Wait here, I'll get it for you.

173
00:07:38,535 --> 00:07:38,974
Okay.

174
00:07:39,975 --> 00:07:40,854
I'll wait.

175
00:08:08,535 --> 00:08:09,214
Nanxi,

176
00:08:09,975 --> 00:08:11,294
do you think you can escape

177
00:08:11,735 --> 00:08:13,414
after bringing down Zhou Quan?

178
00:08:24,775 --> 00:08:25,654
Lan'er,

179
00:08:26,415 --> 00:08:27,614
it's actually you.

180
00:08:33,575 --> 00:08:35,294
Didn't you say you'd wait for me forever?

181
00:08:36,575 --> 00:08:38,054
It's only been a few days.

182
00:08:38,175 --> 00:08:39,574
I thought you weren't coming back.

183
00:08:40,295 --> 00:08:41,534
So you two

184
00:08:43,015 --> 00:08:44,774
were hooking up in the Zhou mansion?

185
00:08:46,135 --> 00:08:47,054
Zhang Jinbao,

186
00:08:47,495 --> 00:08:48,934
you dare betray me?

187
00:08:49,935 --> 00:08:51,054
I betray you?

188
00:08:51,775 --> 00:08:52,574
You murderer,

189
00:08:52,575 --> 00:08:54,254
pretending to be innocent all this time!

190
00:08:55,135 --> 00:08:56,574
Who would actually stay with you?

191
00:08:56,895 --> 00:08:57,254
Get out!

192
00:08:57,815 --> 00:08:58,694
This is my house.

193
00:09:03,575 --> 00:09:04,374
Zhang Jinbao,

194
00:09:04,775 --> 00:09:05,814
what did you say?

195
00:09:06,015 --> 00:09:07,014
Say it again.

196
00:09:08,135 --> 00:09:10,134
You secretly helped the Second Young Master sell opium.

197
00:09:10,655 --> 00:09:12,134
Did you really think I didn't know?

198
00:09:13,135 --> 00:09:14,134
Anything else to say?

199
00:09:14,495 --> 00:09:15,814
I knew you were a murderer.

200
00:09:16,255 --> 00:09:17,894
I didn't want to get too involved with you.

201
00:09:18,535 --> 00:09:19,574
You crazy woman!

202
00:09:20,055 --> 00:09:21,494
Zhang Jinbao,

203
00:09:21,575 --> 00:09:22,694
I'll kill you!

204
00:10:05,695 --> 00:10:06,774
The Qing Dynasty

205
00:10:07,575 --> 00:10:08,654
is not gone.

206
00:10:09,055 --> 00:10:10,414
How could the Qing Dynasty fall?

207
00:10:10,655 --> 00:10:11,254
Princess,

208
00:10:11,375 --> 00:10:12,414
let's go back.

209
00:11:16,895 --> 00:11:17,534
Lan'er?

210
00:11:18,175 --> 00:11:18,894
Master.

211
00:11:20,655 --> 00:11:22,894
Jinbao asked me to give this to you before he died.

212
00:11:23,375 --> 00:11:25,254
He said he was sorry.

213
00:11:28,935 --> 00:11:31,174
Buy two good coffins and bury them both.

214
00:11:31,295 --> 00:11:32,494
Yes, Master.

215
00:11:38,135 --> 00:11:38,694
Go.

216
00:12:04,895 --> 00:12:09,814
[Drowned in the pond. Nanxi.]

217
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:15,054
Those who betray trust

218
00:12:16,055 --> 00:12:17,494
plant the seeds of betrayal,

219
00:12:18,495 --> 00:12:20,534
and will reap a solitary end.

220
00:12:37,775 --> 00:12:39,294
This is the police station.

221
00:12:39,895 --> 00:12:40,934
What are you doing?

222
00:12:41,655 --> 00:12:42,774
This is evidence of your corruption

223
00:12:42,775 --> 00:12:44,814
from Nanxi.

224
00:12:45,575 --> 00:12:46,494
Do you want to read?

225
00:12:47,815 --> 00:12:49,174
How dare you abuse your power

226
00:12:49,415 --> 00:12:51,134
to cover up the slaughter

227
00:12:51,535 --> 00:12:52,494
of innocent people!

228
00:12:53,535 --> 00:12:55,934
No wonder Nanxi has you wrapped around her finger.

229
00:12:57,815 --> 00:12:58,294
What are you

230
00:12:58,295 --> 00:12:59,134
waiting for?

231
00:12:59,575 --> 00:13:00,654
Hurry up and arrest

232
00:13:00,655 --> 00:13:01,574
these intruders

233
00:13:01,575 --> 00:13:02,534
who broke into the police station!

234
00:13:02,655 --> 00:13:03,174
Now!

235
00:13:03,535 --> 00:13:04,414
Hurry!
- Stop!

236
00:13:08,815 --> 00:13:10,174
As law enforcement officers,

237
00:13:10,535 --> 00:13:12,174
pointing guns at civilians?

238
00:13:12,935 --> 00:13:13,894
Put the guns down!

239
00:13:17,535 --> 00:13:18,014
You...

240
00:13:18,495 --> 00:13:19,174
Yu Shi'an.

241
00:13:19,935 --> 00:13:21,694
I treated you well in the past.

242
00:13:22,295 --> 00:13:23,174
Very well?

243
00:13:24,775 --> 00:13:25,654
I still remember

244
00:13:26,295 --> 00:13:28,174
how the brothers risked their lives

245
00:13:28,575 --> 00:13:29,654
for your career advancement.

246
00:13:30,655 --> 00:13:31,294
In the end,

247
00:13:32,495 --> 00:13:34,054
we were just your dogs.

248
00:13:34,895 --> 00:13:35,694
But

249
00:13:36,175 --> 00:13:37,414
who was born

250
00:13:37,575 --> 00:13:38,894
to be a dog?

251
00:13:40,815 --> 00:13:41,574
Brothers,

252
00:13:43,135 --> 00:13:45,534
I'm giving you a chance to see the situation clearly.

253
00:13:47,415 --> 00:13:48,654
Zhou Quan has fallen.

254
00:13:50,695 --> 00:13:52,414
You won't have to be dogs anymore.

255
00:13:52,535 --> 00:13:53,174
Understand?

256
00:13:55,135 --> 00:13:56,654
No one will ever force you

257
00:13:57,255 --> 00:13:58,894
to do things against your conscience.

258
00:14:00,255 --> 00:14:01,414
Nor will anyone

259
00:14:03,175 --> 00:14:04,574
threaten you

260
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:05,934
using your families.

261
00:14:06,935 --> 00:14:09,534
Yeah, that's right.

262
00:14:22,295 --> 00:14:23,014
Take him away.

263
00:14:24,415 --> 00:14:25,134
Thank you,

264
00:14:25,415 --> 00:14:26,254
Shi'an.

265
00:14:34,295 --> 00:14:35,254
I'm pathetic.

266
00:14:35,935 --> 00:14:37,494
I just can't bear to see you wronged.

267
00:14:41,655 --> 00:14:42,814
You didn't have to come today.

268
00:14:42,815 --> 00:14:43,894
Why shouldn't I come?

269
00:14:44,815 --> 00:14:46,654
I don't care if your head gets bashed in,

270
00:14:47,135 --> 00:14:48,254
but I can't accept

271
00:14:48,255 --> 00:14:50,134
her head being pointed at with a gun.

272
00:14:50,295 --> 00:14:50,894
As long as I'm here,

273
00:14:51,495 --> 00:14:52,254
she won't be.

274
00:14:52,695 --> 00:14:53,414
Zhou Yimo,

275
00:14:54,575 --> 00:14:55,374
Yu Shi'an.

276
00:14:56,895 --> 00:14:58,774
My sister's name has finally been cleared.

277
00:15:01,175 --> 00:15:02,014
Thank you both.

278
00:15:12,655 --> 00:15:14,054
We were just joking around.

279
00:15:14,655 --> 00:15:15,174
Right?

280
00:15:16,375 --> 00:15:16,894
Right.

281
00:15:21,655 --> 00:15:22,374
The three of us

282
00:15:23,015 --> 00:15:23,894
living well together

283
00:15:24,255 --> 00:15:25,014
is what matters most.

284
00:15:25,655 --> 00:15:26,254
Agreed?

285
00:15:27,015 --> 00:15:28,054
Who wants to live with you?

286
00:15:28,295 --> 00:15:29,414
Live alone!

287
00:15:31,775 --> 00:15:32,894
I'll live with her.

288
00:15:42,415 --> 00:15:43,774
Wu County Evening News.

289
00:15:44,255 --> 00:15:46,254
Former Wu County Police Chief Zhou Quan

290
00:15:46,375 --> 00:15:47,414
abused his power,

291
00:15:47,575 --> 00:15:48,654
committed murder,

292
00:15:48,655 --> 00:15:49,574
concealment,

293
00:15:49,575 --> 00:15:50,654
and accepted bribes.

294
00:15:50,655 --> 00:15:53,134
Verified by the National Judicial Court,

295
00:15:53,255 --> 00:15:56,414
Zhou Quan has been sentenced to immediate execution.

296
00:15:58,055 --> 00:15:58,894
Sister...

297
00:16:03,255 --> 00:16:04,894
In my dream, you told me

298
00:16:07,135 --> 00:16:08,774
you had let go of the hatred.

299
00:16:11,255 --> 00:16:12,134
Revenge

300
00:16:13,055 --> 00:16:14,374
is just my personal quest.

301
00:16:21,695 --> 00:16:23,014
But I want to say

302
00:16:28,815 --> 00:16:30,814
only by chasing the real killer

303
00:16:33,935 --> 00:16:35,374
can I feel

304
00:16:39,055 --> 00:16:40,054
that you

305
00:16:42,775 --> 00:16:44,374
are still by my side.

306
00:16:47,135 --> 00:16:48,494
Never leaving.

307
00:16:53,415 --> 00:16:54,414
So now

308
00:16:56,655 --> 00:16:57,774
I can't feel

309
00:16:57,775 --> 00:16:59,894
any happiness at all.

310
00:17:01,655 --> 00:17:02,774
Or sense of relief.

311
00:17:06,615 --> 00:17:07,334
Because

312
00:17:12,255 --> 00:17:13,774
it seems like between us

313
00:17:17,095 --> 00:17:19,054
there's no connection left.

314
00:17:23,055 --> 00:17:23,854
Isn't that right?

315
00:17:28,855 --> 00:17:30,534
You gotta live well for me.

316
00:17:43,615 --> 00:17:44,454
Sis.

317
00:17:46,575 --> 00:17:47,614
Live well.

318
00:17:48,375 --> 00:17:49,294
For yourself.

319
00:17:49,935 --> 00:17:51,094
And for my sake too.

320
00:17:52,695 --> 00:17:54,054
Whenever it snows,

321
00:17:54,615 --> 00:17:55,734
I'll come visit you.
